  "detailed_description": "<h1>Early Access Gift</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/ad5b8ab5a3e295502e3f468af9eb02db.avif?t=1771253727\" width=300 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/4eda0488d17fc5d9d5ca5b4ffb9d5a5d.avif?t=1771253727\" width=300 height=80 /></span></p><br><h1>Update Notes</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Features Updates/Changes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More new Tomomons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exotic - Exolink - Exodian Forms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Early Access Gift: Only in Early Access Peroid.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New crazy Characters and Storylines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Tomomon Fusion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modify Tomomon's Chipsets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the Expedition Mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Gachapon (No Microtransaction).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And many more...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/0ea6f38ce7c08b0b77e34fb2c12cc069.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=614 height=345 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/0ea6f38ce7c08b0b77e34fb2c12cc069.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/789dc1405fc76e1d08b44f296a98f858.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/789dc1405fc76e1d08b44f296a98f858.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/789dc1405fc76e1d08b44f296a98f858.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/7a8a7c8ac43fae245a8af857058e4df6.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/7a8a7c8ac43fae245a8af857058e4df6.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/7a8a7c8ac43fae245a8af857058e4df6.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>World of Zento</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you feeling bored? Want to try something new, but it also brings back the old, true good feeling from when you were a child?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come to the Tetron planet, where all this beautifully magical pixel art journey begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zento is the first area you'll encounter on your journey to Tetron. Explore this land with its Tomomons and uncover its many mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring beautiful and colorful pixel art world. (It's actually running around and doing nothing.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travelling across multiple types of environment to discover the lore and the monsters species. (Typical Monster taming gerne, lol.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather valuable materials to craft new items and foods for your Tomomon. (See, your slaves want your food.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building, customizing your own secret base. (Build a nice house to enslave more!!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/72aa5188935c1f91ae3cd65755281adb.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/72aa5188935c1f91ae3cd65755281adb.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/72aa5188935c1f91ae3cd65755281adb.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/10d2ea92339317fe1d1322f6b74a7ea4.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/10d2ea92339317fe1d1322f6b74a7ea4.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/10d2ea92339317fe1d1322f6b74a7ea4.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The TOMOMONs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tomomon are creatures that inhabit the entire planet of Tetron, having appeared and existed for a very long time. Each species of creature has its own unique characteristics, origins, and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enslaving and taming over 200+ Tomomons and making them battle to eternity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Riding them around the big world of Tetron. (or let 'em ride you...)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discovering and forcing Tomomons to evolve for the power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring the Tomomon Fusion for the new power to reach a higher position in society.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interacting with them to manipulate them to get rewards and bonuses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/24c5e48e671f8b0338002bc3b6f68aac.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/24c5e48e671f8b0338002bc3b6f68aac.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/24c5e48e671f8b0338002bc3b6f68aac.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic journey of discovery across Tetron and be a true Tomomon Tamer master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullying weak tamers to earn the victory and become the champion of Zento.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matching up skills to make new strategy to win the engaging 3v3 turn-based battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your build is not effective enough, you will get bullied by the Guardians, Elites, or the Boss. So be warned!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/7a8a7c8ac43fae245a8af857058e4df6.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/7a8a7c8ac43fae245a8af857058e4df6.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/7a8a7c8ac43fae245a8af857058e4df6.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>World of Zento</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you feeling bored? Want to try something new, but it also brings back the old, true good feeling from when you were a child?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come to the Tetron planet, where all this beautifully magical pixel art journey begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zento is the first area you'll encounter on your journey to Tetron. Explore this land with its Tomomons and uncover its many mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring beautiful and colorful pixel art world. (It's actually running around and doing nothing.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travelling across multiple types of environment to discover the lore and the monsters species. (Typical Monster taming gerne, lol.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather valuable materials to craft new items and foods for your Tomomon. (See, your slaves want your food.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building, customizing your own secret base. (Build a nice house to enslave more!!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/72aa5188935c1f91ae3cd65755281adb.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/72aa5188935c1f91ae3cd65755281adb.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/72aa5188935c1f91ae3cd65755281adb.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/10d2ea92339317fe1d1322f6b74a7ea4.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/10d2ea92339317fe1d1322f6b74a7ea4.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/10d2ea92339317fe1d1322f6b74a7ea4.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The TOMOMONs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tomomon are creatures that inhabit the entire planet of Tetron, having appeared and existed for a very long time. Each species of creature has its own unique characteristics, origins, and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enslaving and taming over 200+ Tomomons and making them battle to eternity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Riding them around the big world of Tetron. (or let 'em ride you...)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discovering and forcing Tomomons to evolve for the power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring the Tomomon Fusion for the new power to reach a higher position in society.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interacting with them to manipulate them to get rewards and bonuses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/24c5e48e671f8b0338002bc3b6f68aac.poster.avif?t=1771253727\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/24c5e48e671f8b0338002bc3b6f68aac.webm?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979570/extras/24c5e48e671f8b0338002bc3b6f68aac.mp4?t=1771253727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an epic journey of discovery across Tetron and be a true Tomomon Tamer master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bullying weak tamers to earn the victory and become the champion of Zento.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matching up skills to make new strategy to win the engaging 3v3 turn-based battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your build is not effective enough, you will get bullied by the Guardians, Elites, or the Boss. So be warned!</p>",
